    <item>
      <title>当特朗普的关税使市场处于边缘状态时，美国股票消除了损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-stocks-swoon-as-trump-sows-economic-fear-across-wall-street</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票周一疯狂地挥舞着，S＆amp; P 500指数上台上演了令人惊叹的周转，以消除急剧下降的幅度，因为推进了重型股票繁重的股票和投资组合，重新平衡了暂时对唐纳德·特朗普总统周三的关税宣布的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-stocks-swoon-as-trump-sows-economic-fear-across-wall-street</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 13:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列告诉加沙人在“激烈战斗”之前离开南方</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/israel-tells-gazans-to-leave-border-area-before-intense-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军队告诉巴勒斯坦人在加沙南部的地区离开哈马斯的“激烈战斗”，这是该标志，它计划扩展地面行动，以向激进组织施加压力，以释放仍被俘虏的人质。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/israel-tells-gazans-to-leave-border-area-before-intense-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 10:29:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当交易者权衡特朗普对俄罗斯原油的威胁时，石油的进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）建议美国可能努力减少俄罗斯的原油运输之后，石油上升了，俄罗斯是世界第三大生产商和主要出口商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 23:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
